    "body": "Tried on the latest master:\r\n```\r\n# test.pyx\r\ndef run(a, b=1):\r\n    return a + b\r\n\r\ncdef class A:\r\n    def run(self, a, b=1):\r\n        return a + b\r\n\r\n# app.py\r\nfrom test import A, run\r\nimport inspect\r\n\r\na = A()\r\nprint(inspect.signature(run)) # ok - prints (a, b=1)\r\nprint(inspect.signature(a.run)) # not ok - prints (a, b)\r\nprint(inspect.signature(A.run)) # not ok - prints (self, a, b)\r\n```\r\n",
